title: Happy Third Month Talking
text: Hey bebii bunchinggggg hehehe, happy third month of talking po mah bebii. I just wanted u to know that i am really grateful that i met you, I'm so thankful sayo for staying with me thru our tampuhan, fights and more. Don't think that I will leave you mah bebi cuz I won't leave u kaya and if u think that i have other girls nope i dont have. I am just playing all day here in the house, i really miss u so much mah bebiii mwamwamwamwa i loveyou so much bebiiii. I will stay with u forever and ever. :>>>> happy third month mah bebi and still counting. hihi
